<Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <AppBar position="static">
        <Toolbar>
          <IconButton
            size="large"
            edge="start"
            color="inherit"
            aria-label="menu"
            sx={{ mr: 2 }}

            <MenuIcon />

          <Typography variant="h6" component="div" sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            News

          <Button color="inherit">Login</Button>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </Box>
